19#include <isc/net.h>

21#define RRTYPE_A_ATTRIBUTES (0)

23static inline isc_result_t
24fromtext_in_a(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
25 isc_token_t token;
26 struct in_addr addr;
27 isc_region_t region;
28
29 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_a);
30 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
31
32 UNUSED(type);
33 UNUSED(origin);
34 UNUSED(options);
35 UNUSED(rdclass);
36 UNUSED(callbacks);
37
38 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
39 false));
40
41 if (inet_pton(AF_INET, DNS_AS_STR(token), &addr) != 1)
42 RETTOK(DNS_R_BADDOTTEDQUAD);
43 isc_buffer_availableregion(target, &region);
44 if (region.length < 4)
45 return (ISC_R_NOSPACE);
46 memmove(region.base, &addr, 4);
47 isc_buffer_add(target, 4);
48 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
49}
50
51static inline isc_result_t
52totext_in_a(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
53 isc_region_t region;
54
55 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_a);
56 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
57 REQUIRE(rdata->length == 4);
58
59 UNUSED(tctx);
60
61 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
62 return (inet_totext(AF_INET, &region, target));
63}
64
65static inline isc_result_t
66fromwire_in_a(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
67 isc_region_t sregion;
68 isc_region_t tregion;
69
70 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_a);
71 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
72
73 UNUSED(type);
74 UNUSED(dctx);
75 UNUSED(options);
76 UNUSED(rdclass);
77
78 isc_buffer_activeregion(source, &sregion);
79 isc_buffer_availableregion(target, &tregion);
80 if (sregion.length < 4)
81 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
82 if (tregion.length < 4)
83 return (ISC_R_NOSPACE);
84
85 memmove(tregion.base, sregion.base, 4);
86 isc_buffer_forward(source, 4);
87 isc_buffer_add(target, 4);
88 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
89}
90
91static inline isc_result_t
92towire_in_a(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
93 isc_region_t region;
94
95 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_a);
96 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
97 REQUIRE(rdata->length == 4);
98
99 UNUSED(cctx);
100
101 isc_buffer_availableregion(target, &region);
102 if (region.length < rdata->length)
103 return (ISC_R_NOSPACE);
104 memmove(region.base, rdata->data, rdata->length);
105 isc_buffer_add(target, 4);
106 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
107}
108
109static inline int
110compare_in_a(ARGS_COMPARE) {
111 isc_region_t r1;
112 isc_region_t r2;
113
114 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
115 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
116 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_a);
117 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
118 REQUIRE(rdata1->length == 4);
119 REQUIRE(rdata2->length == 4);
120
121 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &r1);
122 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &r2);
123 return (isc_region_compare(&r1, &r2));
124}
125
126static inline isc_result_t
127fromstruct_in_a(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
128 dns_rdata_in_a_t *a = source;
129 uint32_t n;
130
131 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_a);
132 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
133 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
134 REQUIRE(a->common.rdtype == type);
135 REQUIRE(a->common.rdclass == rdclass);
136
137 UNUSED(type);
138 UNUSED(rdclass);
139
140 n = ntohl(a->in_addr.s_addr);
141
142 return (uint32_tobuffer(n, target));
143}
144
145
146static inline isc_result_t
147tostruct_in_a(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
148 dns_rdata_in_a_t *a = target;
149 uint32_t n;
150 isc_region_t region;
151
152 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_a);
153 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
154 REQUIRE(rdata->length == 4);
155
156 UNUSED(mctx);
157
158 a->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
159 a->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
160 ISC_LINK_INIT(&a->common, link);
161
162 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
163 n = uint32_fromregion(&region);
164 a->in_addr.s_addr = htonl(n);
165
166 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
167}

169static inline void
170freestruct_in_a(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
171 dns_rdata_in_a_t *a = source;
172
173 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
174 REQUIRE(a->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_a);
175 REQUIRE(a->common.rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
176
177 UNUSED(a);
178}

180static inline isc_result_t
181additionaldata_in_a(ARGS_ADDLDATA) {
182 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_a);
183 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
184
185 UNUSED(rdata);

192static inline isc_result_t
193digest_in_a(ARGS_DIGEST) {
194 isc_region_t r;
195
196 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_a);
197 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
198
199 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
200
201 return ((digest)(arg, &r));
202}
203
204static inline bool
205checkowner_in_a(ARGS_CHECKOWNER) {
206 dns_name_t prefix, suffix;
207
208 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_a);
209 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
210
211 UNUSED(type);
212 UNUSED(rdclass);
213
214 /*
215 * Handle Active Diretory gc._msdcs.<forest> name.
216 */
217 if (dns_name_countlabels(name) > 2U) {
218 dns_name_init(&prefix, NULL);
219 dns_name_init(&suffix, NULL);
220 dns_name_split(name, dns_name_countlabels(name) - 2,
221 &prefix, &suffix);
222 if (dns_name_equal(&gc_msdcs, &prefix) &&
223 dns_name_ishostname(&suffix, false))
224 return (true);
225 }
226
227 return (dns_name_ishostname(name, wildcard));
228}
229
230static inline bool
231checknames_in_a(ARGS_CHECKNAMES) {
232
233 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_a);
234 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
235
236 UNUSED(rdata);
237 UNUSED(owner);
238 UNUSED(bad);
239
240 return (true);
241}

243static inline int
244casecompare_in_a(ARGS_COMPARE) {
245 return (compare_in_a(rdata1, rdata2));
246}
